  "text": "This study was conducted on male Dunking Hartley guinea pigs, obtained from an accredited breeding facility (L. Sobota, Městec Králové, Czech Republic). The animals were housed in an approved animal holding facility maintained at a controlled room temperature of [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] O C, with humidity 45 ± 10 %, ventilation, a 12-h light-dark cycle and had free access to water and standard animal food.",
